===Singles===
Prior to September 12, 2016, Music Canada had different certification levels for physical singles and Digital downloads singles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Certification Definitions|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723110958/http://musiccanada.com/certification/|archive-date=July 23, 2016|url=https://musiccanada.com/certification|accessdate=30 September 2017|date=23 July 2016}}</ref> On that date, the digital downloads singles award was discontinued and single awards include digital singles. It also includes streams, where 150 on-demand audio streams from a subscription service equals 1 unit towards certification.<ref name="Certification levels"/>

